Rating: 3
A great idea! I improvised with the technique - after cooking the sausages, I put some preserves in the hot pan until it softened and added a bit of Gulden's spicy mustard to blend, then added sausages to glaze. (Didn't have any rosemary on hand.) It added some delicious zip!

