Rating: 3
Yum! These are easy, delicious and perfect with the eggnog french toast with cranberry-apple compote for a festive Christmas breakfast. I'd cut the oil down to 1 tablespoon at most. The sausages produce some oil while cooking and need to be drained well before glazing. Everybody LOVED them!